us</i> (<i>Cymbeline</i>). The name was borne by  Llywelyn ap Iorwerth  (  1173–1240 ) and his grandson Llywelyn ap Gruffydd (  d. 1282 ), Welsh princes who for a time united their countrymen in North Wales and led opposition to the power of the Norman barons in South Wales and the Marches."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Llywelyn ap Cynwrig was born about 1191, in Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales. She had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Llywelyn ap Cynwrig."},"et":{"about 1191–":"umbes 1191–Surnud","1187–Male":"1187–Surnud","1209–Female":"1209–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1191–Female":"1191–Surnud","about 1191":"umbes 1191","1187":"1187","Abt 1209":"umbes 1209","1209":"1209","1191":"1191","Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales":"Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales","Flintshire, Wales":"Flintshire, Wales, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1191–":"noin 1191–Kuollut","1187–Male":"1187–Kuollut","1209–Female":"1209–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1191–Female":"1191–Kuollut","about 1191":"noin 1191","1187":"1187","Abt 1209":"noin 1209","1209":"1209","1191":"1191","Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales":"Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales","Flintshire, Wales":"Flintshire, Wales, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1191–":"environ 1191–Décédée","1187–Male":"1187–Décédé","1209–Female":"1209–Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1191–Female":"1191–Décédée","about 1191":"environ 1191","1187":"1187","Abt 1209":"environ 1209","1209":"1209","1191":"1191","Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales":"Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Galles","Flintshire, Wales":"Flintshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Llywelyn ap Cynwrig est née environ 1191, à Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Galles. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec Llywelyn ap Cynwrig."},"de":{"about 1191–":"um 1191–Verstorben","1187–Male":"1187–Verstorben","1209–Female":"1209–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1191–Female":"1191–Verstorben","about 1191":"um 1191","1187":"1187","Abt 1209":"um 1209","1209":"1209","1191":"1191","Ystrad, Carmarthenshire, Wales":"Ystrad, Carma